sources.title: Bottom Feeder | Full Movie | Sci-Fi Survival Horror | Tom Sizemore
sources.description:
Bottom Feeder - A group of utility workers are trapped in a series of tunnels which, unfortunately, contain a scientist mutated by his own creation. The creature feeds instantly on a rat, becoming what it has eaten.
2007. Stars: Tom Sizemore, Wendy Anderson, Richard Fitzpatrick
